    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <note>The following incipit and explicit are taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="BAVet82"/>, quoted according to
                    the catalogue description in <bibl><ptr target="bm:GrebTiss1935Codices"/><citedRange unit="page">310</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="title" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab> 
                        ወካዕበ፡ ርኢኩ፡ ለኵሉ፡ አዕማድ፡ ኀበ፡ አቀምክዎሙ፡ ወውስተ፡ እዴሁ፡ ዘሀሎ፤ መስቀሎ፡
                    </ab>
                </div>
                <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                    <ab> 
                        <sic>ወየዓትው፡</sic> አብያቲሆሙ፤ ሕያዋኒሆሙ፡ እንዘ፡ <sic>የአኵትዎ፡</sic> ለወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ገባሬ፡ 
                        መንክራት፤ አሜሃ፡ ሰአሉ፡ ለሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ገብርኤል፡ ወወደይዎ፡ ውስተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያኑ፡ ቅድስት፨ ለዓለመ፤ ዓለም፤ አሜን፨ 
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
